        Our 900+ consultants support you with agility across all your technology transformation
        projects. One goal: to take you further.
      </p>
      <a href="{{ '/en/expertise/' | url }}" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-brand-blue transition hover:text-brand-blue-dark">
        All our expertise <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <ul class="grid list-none gap-3 p-0 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/data-ai/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Data &amp; AI</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/digital-workspace/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Digital Workspace</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/agile/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Agile</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/cloud/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Cloud</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/devops/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">DevOps</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/finance/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Finance</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/software-factory/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Software Factory</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/cybersecurity/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Cybersecurity</a></li>
      <li><a href="{{ '/en/expertise/project-management/' | url }}" class="block rounded-card border border-brand-gray/60 bg-white px-5 py-4 text-center font-medium text-brand-blue shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-brand-blue hover:shadow-soft">Project management</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{# --- 3 entities, 1 governance --- #}
<section class="bg-brand-blue-dark text-brand-ivory">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">3 expert entities, 1 unified governance</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">
      The group brings together three complementary entities, ensuring strategic coherence, sector
      depth and execution continuity.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-10 grid list-none gap-6 p-0 md:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="rounded-card bg-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-gold">Navigacom</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">Strategic information-system architecture.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-card bg-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-gold">Neofin Advisory</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">Transformation of Finance and CIB business lines.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-card bg-white/5 p-8 ring-1 ring-white/10">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-gold">Meritis</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 leading-relaxed text-brand-ivory">Technology engineering and delivery.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

